{"tid":2092753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有黑暴用車輛進行恐怖襲擊","createTime":"2020-07-03T11:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T00:35:10.000Z","uid":105567,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44aba0764bf9985210d99848b72c10c17d03f7eb","tid":2092753,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"記者：「成班人企晒喺度，兜嘢撞埋嚟？」<br />\n<br />\n法庭警員：「呢度係法庭，我而家唔知司機係邊個，你哋退後少少先。」<br />\n<br />\n喺7.1日涉嫌刺傷警員嘅24歲男子由今日警車押送上庭，一般記者會喺門口守候，務求盡量拍攝到喺警車入面嘅情況。但據包括港台在內嘅多間媒體都拍攝到，警車駛入法院車場時未有打燈，並且直接駛向企喺車場前拍攝嘅記者。<br />\n<br />\n由於在場人數不少，記者幾乎走避不及，據報道指，更有電視台攝記因而擦損受傷。而港台記者第一身拍攝到嘅片段中，見到當時情況混亂，警車粗暴駛進車場後，在場多名記者不滿，亦有記者指「成班人企晒喺度，兜嘢撞埋嚟？」。在場法庭警員只回答「呢度係法庭，我而家唔知司機係邊個，你哋退後少少先。」，隨後就進入法庭，未有任何跟進。<br />\n<br />\n港台影片傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=260801868551123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D260801868551123&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=58a23bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=260801868551123</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBCZbqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBCZbqu.jpg&h=459ce387&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aa14cee5af4bf04b44a1c46fce929c3621f0cb2","tid":2092753,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282290578ff8f998f50eacbcc78da9d35dab1a7c","tid":2092753,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"01f843a93250982e403b1a552c61e2d5a9d12aff","tid":2092753,"uid":212884,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"黑人憎唔係冇原因"},{"pid":"be2a18617b31a18ac66955365845ddded84a8c74","tid":2092753,"uid":83335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"會訓斥下"}